      "body": [
        {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "value": "\"I couldn't understand the technology myself being someone who has studied up to a Masters level. It became really hard to function on ground in a techno-centric way. However, when we started focusing on the narratives and songs, the tech just became a side gimmick. And that worked. Making people familiar with such conceptions of technology takes years of ground work. And no one will fund that.\"",
